sourcesContent:
<ion-tabs>

  // Use the icon in ionic's official website to form the bottom navigation bar of the app (G)
  <ion-tab-bar slot="bottom">
    <ion-tab-button tab="tab1" href="/tabs/tab1">
      <ion-icon aria-hidden="true" name="Home"></ion-icon>
      <ion-label>Home</ion-label>
    </ion-tab-button>

    <ion-tab-button tab="tab2" href="/tabs/tab2">
      <ion-icon aria-hidden="true" name="Search"></ion-icon>
      <ion-label>Search</ion-label>
    </ion-tab-button>

    <ion-tab-button tab="tab3" href="/tabs/tab3">
      <ion-icon aria-hidden="true" name="add-circle-sharp"></ion-icon>
      <ion-label>Add</ion-label>
    </ion-tab-button>

    <ion-tab-button tab="tab4" href="/tabs/tab4">
      <ion-icon aria-hidden="true" name="Heart"></ion-icon>
      <ion-label>Featured</ion-label>
    </ion-tab-button>

    <ion-tab-button tab="tab5" href="/tabs/tab5">
      <ion-icon aria-hidden="true" name="Shield"></ion-icon>
      <ion-label>Privacy</ion-label>
    </ion-tab-button>
  </ion-tab-bar>

</ion-tabs>
